{
  "stem": "1033.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No language, no strength, no-- I find that practically inconceivable for anyone to escape from there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no life force.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- there was-- One thing I do remember in Auschwitz that the [INAUDIBLE] Rabbi's son, full of sores-- one of the sons, a tall young boy, covered with sores-- he wouldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember him being taken away, put on one of the trucks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was in October of 1944.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I know he was somebody because the other people deferred to him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was just a young boy, maybe a little older.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He must've been 16.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was 14.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Tall, but covered with sores, skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, no one can knock the power of prayer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It really does take a hold on people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it is-- I don't know that I am insecure about God-- I mean, the conventional God-- because I'm Jewish so I was born insecure, or whether it is something that goes beyond my inheritance.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This boy was very sure of God.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And even though I know that religious people say it's a matter of saving your life, you can eat non-kosher things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm sure that he was gassed and burned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In this [INAUDIBLE] in Landsberg, we worked in underground facilities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I had to carry pebbles in a wheelbarrow from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I really didn't understand what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But there were civilian Germans in charge of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And occasionally, some of them gave me a bit of extra soup.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I could feel that they were kindly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there were others, especially younger ones, who insisted that we march in sync to work, and we brought back people who died from the job.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We pushed them back.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
